# Cloudflare / Netlify rewrites.
# Serve the single-page site for any shared-recipe link; share.js reads the
# /p/<code> payload, decodes it, and scrolls to the #decode section.
# When Oqra IS installed, iOS opens the app before the browser ever loads this.
# Target is "/" (the root index) — OUTSIDE /p/, so the rule can't match its own
# destination (a destination under /p/ would re-trigger /p/* — a loop Cloudflare
# rejects). Clean 200 rewrite, URL stays /p/<code> so the payload is readable.
/p/*  /  200
